OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FEnding sewage dumping will 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fraise water bills - report 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Stopping the dumping of sewage into    
OL,6, rivers and the sea will require huge   
OL,7, infrastructure spending and will       
OL,8, probably push up water bills, according
OL,9, to a new House of Lords report.        
OL,11,FRaw sewage discharge through storm     
OL,12,Foverflows is meant to be an emergency  
OL,13,Flast resort during heavy rain but the  
OL,14,Fgovernment says it happens too often.  
OL,16,FThe system "relies on releasing        
OL,17,Fpolluted water", says the report.      
OL,19,FIt blames successive governments,      
OL,20,Fregulator Ofwat, and water companies.  
